{
  "2359120": {
    "name": "Consume Me",
    "steam_appid": 2359120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做青少年真的太难了。所以我们干脆做了一款游戏，来聊聊这件事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/0ff13760e813b3a33db3f3dd05ca5262.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=780 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/0ff13760e813b3a33db3f3dd05ca5262.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/0ff13760e813b3a33db3f3dd05ca5262.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还记得吗？曾经爸妈、朋友，还有整个社会都联手让你觉得自己又丑、又懒、又笨、又没人爱——尽管你内心，其实藏着一个闪闪发光的灵魂。不记得了？没关系，我们这就通过一款日常向角色扮演游戏，帮你唤起这些记忆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/76cee5381aae36184da1f274e7b25aa3.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/76cee5381aae36184da1f274e7b25aa3.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/76cee5381aae36184da1f274e7b25aa3.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Consume Me》中，你将扮演珍妮，一名正值青春年华、坠入爱河、即将迈入高三生活的少女。你需要精打细算地安排每天的行程，努力让自己发光发亮！解开节食减肥的拼图难题！在学习的道路上闪避各种诱惑干扰！帮妈妈做家务换点零花钱，而且工资还远低于最低时薪！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7a1b95ed7f834751273fac66f5493e71.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=780 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7a1b95ed7f834751273fac66f5493e71.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7a1b95ed7f834751273fac66f5493e71.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/51161918e1439d4eb3355db73292d3c9.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=780 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/51161918e1439d4eb3355db73292d3c9.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/51161918e1439d4eb3355db73292d3c9.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能成功追到梦中的男神吗？还有能不能守住这段感情？你能否为自己规划一条可继续前进的未来之路？你的行程还能再塞下一个待办清单目标吗？还是早就超过负荷了？更重要的是这一切到底有没有意义？不管是游戏里，还是现实中都一样。我在这里就不剧透故事了，免费小提示：如果你手头有点闲钱，去街角咖啡店坐坐，点一杯咖啡，说不定就能赚到额外的空闲时间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/3358328f9be43b83ac74514c39228711.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=780 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/3358328f9be43b83ac74514c39228711.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/3358328f9be43b83ac74514c39228711.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一段幽默又略带黑暗的成长故事</strong>：你会忍不住笑出声，也可能突然眼眶湿润，甚至莫名其妙地觉得饿……而这一切，有时候还会同时发生！抱歉啦！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一顿饭都是一场拼图</strong>：午饭得吃，但不能吃太多。也不能吃太少。不想吃的就扔给家里的小狗吧。没关系，<strong><i>她</i></strong>没在节食！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精彩的策略抉择体验</strong>：时间有限，但有无限的事情等着去做？这种经典设计带来了一个终极问题：你该怎么分配自己的时间？这个问题將伴隨着...你人生的每一天！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>获得强力装备</strong>：精挑细选你的穿搭，让自己光鲜亮丽地出现在每个重要场合。但要注意，本游戏的装备只有一天寿命，直到你完成那个古老而神秘的仪式...「洗衣服」。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过 13 种的结局：</strong>大部份都是坏结局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/9431c59dc6cdf255dd837ea7d7ae7f65.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/9431c59dc6cdf255dd837ea7d7ae7f65.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/9431c59dc6cdf255dd837ea7d7ae7f65.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7c51df888d0af72a20e9428695a6fc49.poster.avif?t=1758745344\" width=780 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7c51df888d0af72a20e9428695a6fc49.webm?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359120/extras/7c51df888d0af72a20e9428695a6fc49.mp4?t=1758745344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
